350
00:16:05,930 --> 00:16:06,840
Three letters.
三封信

351
00:16:06,900 --> 00:16:07,920
Three stages.
三個階段

352
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:09,510
I know what you're thinking,Jethro,
我知道你在想什麼 Jethro

