但我敢說答案一定能在Timothy的新書裡找到

364
00:16:35,790 --> 00:16:37,640
The writer believes that
寫信人相信

365
00:16:37,660 --> 00:16:41,850
Timothy's fiction is very much real.
Timothy的小說是真實的

366
00:16:56,720 --> 00:16:58,300
Tony,you about...
Tony 你快...

367
00:17:05,170 --> 00:17:06,280
Done.
好了

368
00:17:07,660 --> 00:17:08,590
So?
怎樣?

369
00:17:08,900 --> 00:17:10,260
I'm confused.
我很困惑

370
00:17:11,710 --> 00:17:13,110
This isn't a critique,okay?
不是要你評論 知道嗎?

371
00:17:13,190 --> 00:17:14,910
We're trying to find something useful...
我們正在尋找有用的線索...

372
00:17:16,200 --> 00:17:17,620
Confused by what?
為了什麼困惑?

373
00:17:18,790 --> 00:17:22,970
The plot,the back story, pretty much everything.
