374
00:17:23,430 --> 00:17:25,140
The whole thing doesn't make sense.
整個故事簡直不知講什麼

375
00:17:26,530 --> 00:17:28,000
Ziva,what about you?
Ziva 你呢?

376
00:17:29,290 --> 00:17:31,380
Well,not as confused as Tony.
呃 沒有Tony那麼困惑

377
00:17:31,990 --> 00:17:33,070
Well,I haven't finished it yet.
呃 我還沒寫完

378
00:17:33,100 --> 00:17:34,470
It's just a rough draft.
這只是一個粗稿

379
00:17:34,510 --> 00:17:36,070
Very rough.
真的很粗

380
00:17:36,830 --> 00:17:38,360
I'm sorry,McGee.
對不起 McGee

381
00:17:38,450 --> 00:17:40,060
Who's the killer,anyway?
那 兇手是誰?

382
00:17:40,160 --> 00:17:41,420
I don't know yet.
我還不知道

383
00:17:41,900 --> 00:17:42,600
There's your problem.
這就是你的問題了

384
00:17:42,640 --> 00:17:45,600
I mean,yeah,you always have to know where your story is going.
我意思是 你得一直清楚你故事的走向

