胸部和腹部的刀傷一摸一樣

433
00:20:03,160 --> 00:20:07,960
It appears that Petty Officer Cove may have put up a bit of a struggle.
這表明士官Cove曾經掙扎過一陣

434
00:20:08,230 --> 00:20:12,590
Note the remnants of skin tissue and blood under the fingernails..
從指甲裡的皮膚殘留組織 和血跡可以看出來

435
00:20:12,640 --> 00:20:16,930
Both men have been deceased for less than 24 hours.
兩個人的死亡時間都不超過24小時

436
00:20:17,060 --> 00:20:18,810
That is not all they have in common,Ducky.
這不是他們唯一的共同點 Ducky

437
00:20:18,860 --> 00:20:21,620
They're also both characters in McGeek's next book.
他們都是McGee下本書的角色

438
00:20:21,680 --> 00:20:25,140
Yes. From what I hear, Timothy, in your next novel,
對 我聽說了 Timothy 在你下本小說裡

439
00:20:25,190 --> 00:20:27,930
L.J. Tibbs has a love interest.
L.J. Tibbs 有一段曖昧關係

440
00:20:28,950 --> 00:20:29,950
Yes.
對

441
00:20:30,070 --> 00:20:31,490
I hear that it's an Army...
我聽說是個軍隊...

442
00:20:31,550 --> 00:20:33,800
Ducky,I don't think we need to talk about that.
Ducky 我覺得我們不該討論這個

443
00:20:33,850 --> 00:20:36,420
<i>Army what? McGee?
軍隊的什麼? McGee?</i>

