00:20:49,960 --> 00:20:52,430
Yes,well,that's where things get interesting,Jethro.
對 有趣的是 Jethro

449
00:20:52,590 --> 00:20:57,100
Both wounds are circular about one inch in diameter.
兩個傷口都是直徑大約一英吋的圓形

450
00:20:57,330 --> 00:20:58,600
- Javelin. - Javelin.
- 標槍 - 標槍

451
00:20:58,700 --> 00:20:59,920
Chapter Four.
第四章

452
00:20:59,970 --> 00:21:01,780
My characters Cameron Meyer and Jared Brenner—
我書裡的Cameron Meyer和Jared Brenner...

