也要視環境而...

461
00:21:25,010 --> 00:21:26,460
Oh,dear.
哦 天

462
00:21:27,100 --> 00:21:29,610
<i>Now I'm gonna have to read his new book.
現在我得去讀讀他的新書了</i>

463
00:21:30,590 --> 00:21:33,590
Petty Officer Darren Cove and Adrian Corbett,
士官Darren Cove和Adrian Corbett

