他的工作是什麼?

474
00:21:53,870 --> 00:21:55,450
Valet at a steakhouse.
牛排餐館的侍應

475
00:21:55,500 --> 00:21:57,270
But I did change the name of the restaurant.
但我改掉了餐館的名字

476
00:21:57,330 --> 00:21:59,320
From Alfonso's to fredo's.
從Alfonso改成Afredo

477
00:21:59,390 --> 00:22:01,800
Don't need to be Sherlock Holmes to figure that one out.
不一定只有福爾摩斯才猜得到

478
00:22:01,860 --> 00:22:03,840
