00:22:34,680 --> 00:22:37,590
27 javelins sold in the DC area in the past six months.
特區過去六個月賣出了27根標槍

494
00:22:37,660 --> 00:22:39,780
21 were paid for by credit cards,
21根是用信用卡付帳的

495
00:22:39,800 --> 00:22:41,910
all by track coaches and athletic directors.
買家都是田徑教練和運動員指導

496
00:22:41,950 --> 00:22:43,150
at about the last six?
那剩下六個呢?

497
00:22:43,190 --> 00:22:44,600
Cash transactions.
現金交易

498
00:22:46,420 --> 00:22:47,380
Yeah. Gibbs.
對 Gibbs

499
00:22:47,400 --> 00:22:48,290
Got them for you,Gibbs.
找到了 Gibbs

500
00:22:48,350 --> 00:22:49,810
Got it,Abs. We'll be right down.
知道了 Abs 我們馬上下去

501
00:22:49,840 --> 00:22:50,740
Go,go.
走 走

502
00:22:52,290 --> 00:22:53,310
Not you.
你不用

503
00:22:55,360 --> 00:22:57,380
Two men are dead because of me,boss.
兩個人因為我而死了 頭

504
00:22:57,570 --> 00:22:59,030
You got a javelin,McGee?
你有標槍嗎 McGee?

505
00:22:59,300 --> 00:23:00,990
No,but I own a typewriter.
不 但我有個打字機

506
00:23:02,350 --> 00:23:04,850
It's a typewriter,not a shotgun.
那是個打字機 不是手槍

507
00:23:04,910 --> 00:23:06,070
It cost two men their lives
它送掉了兩條人命

508
00:23:06,110 --> 00:23:09,280
because I based my fictional book on real people.
就因為我在小說裡用了真人做原型

509
00:23:09,520 --> 00:23:10,660
Then put these on.
那銬上這個

510
00:23:13,160 --> 00:23:14,770
You just confessed,right?
你剛剛承認了 不是嗎?

511
00:23:14,840 --> 00:23:16,240
Not exactly.
不完全是這樣

512
00:23:16,350 --> 00:23:17,930
There's no mid ground,McGee.
沒有中間地帶 McGee

513
00:23:17,970 --> 00:23:21,070
