00:24:37,920 --> 00:24:39,270
A little birdie,huh?
小小鳥?

546
00:24:39,380 --> 00:24:43,420
And don't even ask because I will not reveal my source evenf you torture me.
別問 因為就算你嚴刑逼供 我也不會告訴你我從哪裡知道的

