I told you already,I wasn't running.
我告訴你了 我沒在逃跑

649
00:30:04,000 --> 00:30:05,920
I was late for an appointment.
而是約會遲到了

650
00:30:05,990 --> 00:30:07,180
And murder.
加上謀殺

651
00:30:09,620 --> 00:30:11,510
You think I murdered someone?
你認為我殺人了?

652
00:30:14,400 --> 00:30:18,180
Their names are Petty Officer Darren Cove and Adrian Corbett.
他們是士官Darren Cove和Adrian Corbett

653
