Never heard of 'em.
從沒聽說過

654
00:30:20,150 --> 00:30:21,340
Okay.
好吧

655
00:30:21,930 --> 00:30:25,870
Well, how about Cameron Meyer and Jared Brenner?
那Cameron Meyer和Jared Brenner呢?

656
