Have you heard of them?
聽說過他們嗎?

657
00:30:26,950 --> 00:30:28,130
I think so.
我覺得是

658
00:30:28,920 --> 00:30:31,580
They're characters in Tim's next book.
他們是Tim下一本書裡的角色

659
00:30:32,630 --> 00:30:34,290
A book someone is killing over.
有人殺死了書裡的人

660
