He said you told him to mail the letters back to the agency.
說你讓他把信件寄回出版社

666
00:30:52,760 --> 00:30:54,230
Well,I can explain.
我可以解釋

667
00:30:54,390 --> 00:30:56,630
Well,I sure hope .
我當然希望如此

668
00:30:56,680 --> 00:30:58,390
I wrote the letters,
我寫這些信

669
00:30:58,440 --> 00:31:00,660
but only to create a bigger buzz.
只不過是為了引起轟動

670
00:31:00,700 --> 00:31:01,990
Stalkers mean more press.
跟蹤狂意味著更多發行量

671
