她知道怎麼把故事講得生動

678
00:31:20,450 --> 00:31:21,700
I'm with Ziva.
我同意Ziva

679
00:31:22,370 --> 00:31:24,840
This woman lives to sell books.
這女人靠售書為生

680
00:31:24,920 --> 00:31:26,220
Look,it may sound unorthodox,
聽著 也許聽起來很陰險

681
00:31:26,300 --> 00:31:28,300
but I do one interview about those letters
但我為一些類似信件做了次採訪

682
00:31:28,360 --> 00:31:30,400
and Gemcity's book sales jump through the roof.
Gemcity的書的銷量就一路飆升

683
00:31:30,450 --> 00:31:32,130
