他是你的出版商

698
00:32:08,580 --> 00:32:09,590
You tell me.
你說呢

699
00:32:10,250 --> 00:32:11,860
I think she's telling the truth.
我認為她吐露的是實情

700
00:32:12,170 --> 00:32:13,470
That makes two of us.
我跟你一樣想法

701
00:32:13,690 --> 00:32:18,350
I compared Crawhaw's DNA to the mystery blood pulled off of Petty Officer Cove.
